OL,3,CSailor who helped bring home wrongly
OL,4,Cimprisoned guards receives medal
OL,6,FA sailor who helped bring home a group
OL,7,Fof British maritime security guards
OL,8,Fwrongly jailed in India has been
OL,9,Fawarded a medal.
OL,11,FSteven Jones, 52, is among nine new
OL,12,Frecipients of the Merchant Navy Medal,
OL,13,Fthe Department for Transport (DfT)
OL,14,Fannounced.
OL,16,FMr Jones, from Wirral, campaigned for
OL,17,Fthe freedom of six British men jailed
OL,18,Fin India after being arrested in
OL,19,FOctober 2013 on weapons charges.
