OL,3,CSailor who helped bring home wrongly
OL,4,Cimprisoned guards receives medal
OL,6,FThey had been working as guards on a
OL,7,Fship combatting piracy in the Indian
OL,8,FOcean.
OL,10,FMr Jones raised the profile of the so-
OL,11,Fcalled Chennai Six, exposing the
OL,12,Finjustice and the challenging
OL,13,Fconditions they faced.
OL,15,FThe men later won an appeal against
OL,16,Ftheir convictions in November 2017 and
OL,17,Fwere given permission to leave India.
