OL,6,FMr Jones also champions mental health
OL,7,Fand created the Seafarers Happiness
OL,8,FIndex in 2015, which monitors the mood
OL,9,Fof maritime workers.
OL,11,FThis helps shipping companies and
OL,12,Forganisations to provide targeted
OL,13,Fsupport.
OL,15,FMr Jones said: "I'm thrilled to
OL,16,Freceive the Merchant Navy Medal.
OL,18,F"It's absolutely vital that seafarers
OL,19,Fhave a voice, are listened to by the
OL,20,Findustry and seen by society.
