OL,6,F"I'm glad I am able to shine a light
OL,7,Fon the important work that seafarers
OL,8,Fdo and I'll continue to champion them
OL,9,Fin the years to come."
OL,11,FMaritime minister Mike Kane said:
OL,12,F"It's fantastic to see these nine
OL,13,Fremarkable sailors receive this very
OL,14,Fspecial award ` the highest in the
OL,15,Findustry.
OL,17,F"Their dedication, bravery and
OL,18,Ffortitude is truly inspiring and shows
OL,19,Fthe very best of UK maritime.
